/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/99bd27de3190de4e1fe232e727a0743d.jpg", "title": "MultiVersus: What Do Returning Players Get?", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-05-22T20:10:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/22d79c863d6dbc1866eab6cf829a7151.jpg\" /><p>WB Games and Rocksteady\u2019s online supervillain looter-shooter, <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/suicide-squad-justice-league-review-is-it-good-batman-1851222047\">Suicide Squad: Kill The Justice League</a>, received some new skins ahead of the game\u2019s upcoming <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://www.suicidesquadgame.com/en-us/community/season-1-episode-2-patch-notes\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">season 1 episode 2 update</a>. But the new skins haven\u2019t gone over well with the game\u2019s remaining players who aren\u2019t sure how much longer they can keep playing. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/suicide-squad-bad-skins-joker-titan-shop-season-1-patch-1851494445\">Read more...</a></p>", "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/suicide-squad-bad-skins-joker-titan-shop-season-1-patch-1851494445", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/22d79c863d6dbc1866eab6cf829a7151.jpg", "title": "Suicide Squad's Remaining Players Rewarded With Ugly Arkham Skins", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_publi